@jacquelinekay found this bug when trying to move static models via the `ArrangePlugin`. Her particular scenario had lots of models (like the [wood_block_stack](#!/osrf/gazebo_models/src/toy_stack/wood_block_stack/model.sdf)), so the system was under heavy load. The server would always register the object move, but it wasn't always reflected in the GUI visual location.

I think static models may only send one pose update message, so perhaps the message got dropped?

